Package application

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    Representation for an Account including holder, balance, open date and necessary methods
    AccountDatabase
    Representation of an Account Database including list of accounts, increment value, size and necessary methods
    Checking
    Representation of a Checking account including if its direct deposit and necessary methods extends Account class
    Controller
    Controller Class to link functionality to buttons/input on GUI Contains action methods and helper methods for each input source
    Date
    Representation of a Date including year, month, day and necessary methods
    Main
    Driver Class to link fxml and set the stage
    MoneyMarket
    Representation of a Money Market account including the number of withdrawals and necessary methods extends Account class
    Profile
    Representation of Profile including first name, last name and necessary methods
    Savings
    Representation of a Savings account including if its loyal and necessary methods extends Account class
